OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1780747879
OL,3,CHelp to combat the physical and mental
OL,4,Ctolls on farmers in the spotlight
OL,6,FThe Prince of Wales has thrown his
OL,7,Fpersonal support behind efforts to
OL,8,Fhelp farmers in Cornwall suffering
OL,9,Fwith their mental health.
OL,11,FHe personally asked for the Duchy of
OL,12,FCornwall to sponsor this year's Mental
OL,13,FHealth Hub at the Royal Cornwall Show.
OL,15,FIts widely recognised agriculture can
OL,16,Fhave both a physical and mental toll
OL,17,Fon farmers.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
