PN,43502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1780747879
OL,3,CHelp to combat the physical and mental
OL,4,Ctolls on farmers in the spotlight
OL,6,FFigures from the Farm Safety
OL,7,FFoundation's Mind Your Head project
OL,8,Frevealed that 47 people from the
OL,9,Ffarming community took their own lives
OL,10,Fin 2024.
OL,12,FIn 2025, for the first time, a wide
OL,13,Frange of charities involved with
OL,14,Fmental health joined forces to have a
OL,15,FMental Health Hub at the Royal
OL,16,FCornwall Show.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1780747879
OL,3,CHelp to combat the physical and mental
OL,4,Ctolls on farmers in the spotlight
OL,6,FThis year that hub has returned. It
OL,7,Fhas been organised by the Cornish
OL,8,Fmental health charity Pentreath, with
OL,9,Fthe aim of helping and signposting
OL,10,Fpeople in the farming community to the
OL,11,Fright support.
OL,13,FOther charities involved in the
OL,14,Fproject include Man Down, Georgia's
OL,15,FVoice, Papyrus, Sunrise Cornwall and
OL,16,Fthe Cornwall Rural Community Charity.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1780747879
OL,3,CHelp to combat the physical and mental
OL,4,Ctolls on farmers in the spotlight
OL,6,FKatie Mutton, Communication and
OL,7,FEngagement Co-ordinator from Pentreath
OL,8,Fsaid: "If you think of the farmers,
OL,9,Fthey are working on their farm day in
OL,10,Fday out every single day, some of them
OL,11,Fonly leave their farm for Royal
OL,12,FCornwall.
OL,14,F"Overall I think people are more open
OL,15,Fabout speaking about mental health and
OL,16,Fthey're more open to learning about
OL,17,Fit, which is what we want.
OL,26,@pD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1780747879
OL,3,CHelp to combat the physical and mental
OL,4,Ctolls on farmers in the spotlight
OL,6,F"I was talking to someone yesterday, 1
OL,7,Fin 4 people struggle with their mental
OL,8,Fwellbeing, so if you are not going to
OL,9,Fstruggle personally, you are going to
OL,10,Fknow somebody who is, so it's really
OL,11,Fimportant to educate people and let
OL,12,Fpeople know what's out there and where
OL,13,Fthey can get support from if needed."
OL,15,FAnother group at the Mental Health Hub
OL,16,Fis Farm Cornwall which supports more
OL,17,Fthan 600 farmers across the Duchy.
OL,26,@uD@eO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1780747879
OL,3,CHelp to combat the physical and mental
OL,4,Ctolls on farmers in the spotlight
OL,6,FThe charity is seeing an increasing
OL,7,Fnumber of farmers with financial
OL,8,Fworries and are continuing to help
OL,9,Fthem through the issues.
OL,11,FFor many it's an added stress because
OL,12,Ftheir homes and legacies are linked to
OL,13,Ftheir farm.
OL,15,FLouise Davis, farm advisor and
OL,16,Foutreach worker for Farm Cornwall
OL,17,Fsaid: "Often it's generations of
OL,18,Ffamilies that we're talking about
OL,19,Fhere, it's not as simple as giving up
OL,20,Fa day job.
OL,26,@yD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1780747879
OL,3,CHelp to combat the physical and mental
OL,4,Ctolls on farmers in the spotlight
OL,6,F"This is people's homes and it's often
OL,7,Fa future they had planned out so it's
OL,8,Fvery difficult for people to decide
OL,9,Fwhat to do, they have to factor in the
OL,10,Fwhole family not just themselves and
OL,11,Ffor many it's a very difficult and
OL,12,Femotional time, so Farm Cornwall can
OL,13,Fsupport farmers through this journey.
OL,15,F"We do work through lots of partner
OL,16,Fagencies so if we think it is
OL,17,Fsomething better dealt with by someone
OL,18,Felse we can refer, we all communicate
OL,19,Fand talk to each other, we all want
OL,20,Fthe best outcome for the farmers"
OL,26,@|D@aO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
