OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1780747879
OL,3,CHelp to combat the physical and mental
OL,4,Ctolls on farmers in the spotlight
OL,6,FIt's not just a mental toll that
OL,7,Faffects the farming industry, it's
OL,8,Falso a physical one. Just one in 100
OL,9,Fpeople work in agriculture, but it
OL,10,Faccounts for one in five workplace
OL,11,Ffatalities.
OL,13,FThe Royal Agricultural Benevolent
OL,14,FInstitution charity, RABI, used the
OL,15,FRoyal Cornwall Show to launch their
OL,16,Fnew 'FarmersAid' app.
OL,18,FThe app gives clear, step-by-step
OL,19,Fsupport following a serious on-farm
OL,20,Faccident.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1780747879
OL,3,CHelp to combat the physical and mental
OL,4,Ctolls on farmers in the spotlight
OL,6,FThe charity says it has been developed
OL,7,Fbecause of the realities of rural
OL,8,Ffarming environments, particularly in
OL,9,FDevon and Cornwall, with people often
OL,10,Fworking alone and a considerable
OL,11,Fdistance from emergency services.
OL,13,FProfessor Stuart Maitland-Knibb, a
OL,14,Fleading expert in rural emergency
OL,15,Fmedicine, said: "We're absolutely sure
OL,16,Fthis will save lives.
OL,26,@wD@QOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1780747879
OL,3,CHelp to combat the physical and mental
OL,4,Ctolls on farmers in the spotlight
OL,6,F"Lives are being unnecessarily lost at
OL,7,Fthe moment because people aren't able
OL,8,Fto do the things they need to do to
OL,9,Fsave a life because the knowledge just
OL,10,Fisn't there.
OL,12,F"It's surprising it hasn't been done
OL,13,Fbefore but fantastic that we're doing
OL,14,Fit now."
OL,16,FThe app is designed to help people
OL,17,Ftake calm, practical action while
OL,18,Femergency services are on the way.
OL,26,@vD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1780747879
OL,3,CHelp to combat the physical and mental
OL,4,Ctolls on farmers in the spotlight
OL,6,FThe charity is keen to stress it does
OL,7,Fnot replace calling 999 or
OL,8,Fprofessional medical care.
OL,10,FInstead 'FarmersAid' is designed to
OL,11,Fhelp in the critical window where
OL,12,Fearly action can directly influence
OL,13,Fsurvival outcomes. In scenarios such
OL,14,Fas severe bleeding, intervention
OL,15,Fwithin 60 to 90 seconds can be the
OL,16,Fdifference between life and death.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1780747879
OL,3,CHelp to combat the physical and mental
OL,4,Ctolls on farmers in the spotlight
OL,6,FAlicia Chivers, Chief Executive at
OL,7,FRABI, said: "It's not to take the
OL,8,Fplace of the emergency services, so
OL,9,Fthe first thing the app will do is to
OL,10,Ftell you to dial 999, but it is then
OL,11,Fto give the best possible outcome.
OL,13,F"What happens in the platinum 10
OL,14,Fminutes post the accident can save
OL,15,Fwhile the emergency services are on
OL,16,Ftheir way."
OL,18,FThe app is available to download on
OL,19,Fboth Apple Store and Google Play
OL,26,@oD@MOUxD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/12
